                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18361128-38-offence-1 t18361128-cd-31"></join>16th of May</rs>, 3 shillings, 1 sixpence, and 2 pence; the monies of <persName id="t18361128-name-301" type="victimName">
